1
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:54,119
I wasn't in the palace

2
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:55,920
when it happened.

3
00:00:57,119 --> 00:00:58,560
He was killed by a demon,

4
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,240
his death was brutal.

5
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,560
Because of this,

6
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:06,920
his death is a forbidden topic in the palace.

7
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:10,200
Father even ordered all who knew to be killed,

8
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,799
and everything of his to be burned.

9
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:16,200
This is the only thing I managed to save.

10
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,480
So,

11
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,599
you hate demons so much

12
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:22,159
just to avenge your brother's death?

13
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:23,400
Yes.

14
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,159
The demon who killed my brother

15
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,560
is still at large.

16
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:30,159
I swore to kill every demon

17
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:32,159
in the world

18
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,680
to avenge him.

19
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,560
To avenge one man's death,

20
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:39,560
you want to kill millions of demons.

21
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,599
Shen Que,

22
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:43,840
you're no better than the demon you hate.

23
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,280
19 in total.

24
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,079
Take them.

25
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,200
One is missing.

26
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,079
One is missing.

27
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:12,919
I can't find

28
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:14,479
the last one.

29
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,479
Then stop looking.

30
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,800
Maybe it's fate.

31
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:23,280
Perhaps my brother blames me for not avenging him.

32
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,319
A thought brings bloom,

33
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,000
another brings fall.

34
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,639
Let go of a thought,

35
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,759
and all is at ease.

36
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,199
Your Highness,

37
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:39,000
I think this is what your brother

38
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,240
wants you to let go of your obsession

39
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,560
in this way.

40
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,800
Thank you, Miss Meng.

41
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,680
It's late.

42
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,039
Have a good rest.

43
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:03,919
Your Highness.

44
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,479
You must be tired today.

45
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,719
Have a good rest.

46
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:27,240
There are dangers in the mountains.

47
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,960
I'm afraid there will be evil spirits.

48
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,520
Don't worry.

49
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,960
I'll stay up all night outside

50
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,479
to keep you safe.

51
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:01,800
Uh...

52
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,080
Are you tired?

53
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,120
Go rest.

54
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,919
Okay.

55
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,800
Your Highness,

56
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,639
the Vice Minister of Revenue

57
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,919
ignored your order

58
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,879
and took away Ruan Wei's body.

59
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:21,920
Let him come to see me.

60
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,519
Yes.

61
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:27,040
I came to see Your Highness.

62
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,279
I haven't changed my mourning clothes.

63
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:30,040
Please forgive me.

64
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:30,839
Lord Ruan,

65
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:33,399
the case of the demon is still under investigation.

66
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,680
The body of Ruan Wei is the key to the case.

67
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,720
But you took it back.

68
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,959
Who gave you the guts?

69
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:44,959
It's Your Highness' duty to eradicate the demon.

70
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,519
My son is just a dead civilian.

71
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,319
As his father,

72
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:51,879
I can't bear to see him suffer again.

73
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:52,639
Nonsense!

74
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:58,040
The dead are dead.

75
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,720
How can he suffer again?

76
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:02,240
As a court official,

77
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,240
you're so ignorant of the big picture.

78
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,720
Ignorant of the big picture?

79
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:09,199
Your Highness, you're holding onto my son's body

80
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,639
simply because his tragic death

81
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,199
mirrors that of Prince Qi.

82
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,319
Shut up!

83
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:16,639
You claim to be devoted to demon hunting,

84
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:20,240
but it's all because Prince Qi's death was linked to demons.

85
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:22,240
You claim to benefit the people,

86
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:26,040
but you just take the opportunity to avenge your brother's death.

87
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,839
Is this your so-called righteousness?

88
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:38,120
You're not qualified to lecture me.

89
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:41,759
I'm old,

90
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:44,040
but I'll try my best

91
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:48,040
to give my son a decent burial.

92
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:50,439
The funeral is not over,

93
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,879
please

94
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,879
don't bother me again.

95
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,199
My Lord,

96
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:02,560
I've got news about the girl whom the young master liked.

97
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,160
Who is she?

98
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:07,480
A Nuo Opera performer,

99
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,680
not from a noble family.

100
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,240
Never mind.

101
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,839
As long as my son likes her.

102
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,199
Now,

103
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:16,399
where is she?

104
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,519
It's quite strange.

105
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,759
She's being kept in Prince Xian's mansion.

106
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,160
Hmph!

107
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,639
Shen Que,

108
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,879
heartless and unfaithful.

109
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,600
He's always against me.

110
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:27,879
It seems that

111
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,839
I have to teach him a lesson.

112
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:32,399
Bring her here as soon as possible.

113
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:33,800
Yes.

114
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,519
The news from the spy.

115
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:39,279
Meng Li went to the Nether Mountain.

116
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,399
The Nether Mountain is so dangerous.

117
00:06:44,079 --> 00:06:45,000
Did she go there alone?

118
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:46,000
Yes.

119
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:51,800
Your Highness.

120
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,480
You...

121
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,600
I found

122
00:07:34,319 --> 00:07:35,399
the last bead.

123
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,639
You went to Nether Mountain

124
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,319
just for this bead?

125
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,759
Yesterday, you trusted me

126
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,959
and told me the story behind it.

127
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,079
Today,

128
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,879
I want to help you.

129
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,800
The mountain is steep,

130
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,680
and demons are rampant.

131
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,600
It's very dangerous.

132
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:57,720
Is it worth it

133
00:07:58,639 --> 00:07:59,360
is it worth it?

134
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,480
To help you retrieve something precious,

135
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,360
a bit of hardship

136
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:08,720
is worth it.

137
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,159
[Shen Que's attitude towards me has changed,]

138
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:43,559
[my plan seems to be working.]

139
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:48,320
[But this may not unlock the deeper dream.]

140
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,639
[I might need to change my approach.]

141
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:57,120
You are Meng Li from the Nuo Opera Troupe.

142
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:59,440
Vice Minister of Revenue, Lord Ruan, requests your presence.

143
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,080
[If Shen Que's desire for me]

144
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,759
[isn't strong enough to unlock the deeper dream,]

145
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:12,399
[I need to make him fall for me.]

146
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,519
[I'll turn the tables.]

147
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:17,600
[I'll try the hero rescuing the beauty.]

148
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:36,080
[Disguise yourself as a carrier pigeon and deliver the letter to Qingdu Temple.]

149
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,639
[Remember to stay in character.]

150
00:10:48,639 --> 00:10:49,480
[Okay.]

151
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,840
You're so handsome.

152
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,799
No wonder my son likes you.

153
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,000
Today

154
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:58,000
is the day you marry my son.

155
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:06,559
This thing can seal my demon power.

156
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,919
Good daughter-in-law.

157
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:10,759
This is a gift for you.

158
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,080
I've done nothing to you.

159
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,679
Why are you doing this?

160
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,360
You should feel honored.

161
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,000
With your lowly status,

162
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:18,639
you wouldn't

163
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,000
have married my son

164
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,039
even if you'd done good deeds for generations.

165
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,320
Guards!

166
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:24,879
Go get the bride!

167
00:11:25,799 --> 00:11:28,000
Go get the bride!
